::Aerotaur::
       He frowns in contemplation.  "I'm not sure what we'll do then.  But I 
think we should find a new base, somewhere hidden away from everyone else.  
Then the rest of the Taurusoids and I will go track down Chaostaur.  If we 
can reprogram him, we'll have our own gestalt to defend us."
